Package org.e2immu.annotation

Annotation Type E1Container

@Retention(CLASS)
@Target({FIELD,PARAMETER,METHOD,TYPE})
public @interface E1Container
Annotation marking that the type is effectively or eventually level 1 immutable (all fields are (eventually) @Final), and the type is a container.

  • Optional Element Summary

    Optional Elements
    Modifier and Type Optional Element Description
    boolean absent  
    java.lang.String after  
    boolean contract  

  • Element Details

    • absent

      boolean absent
      Default:

    • contract

      boolean contract
      Default:
      false

    • after

      java.lang.String after
      Returns:
      when the type is effectively level 1 immutable, set the empty string. When it is eventually level 1 immutable, return a comma-separated list of strings from @Mark values on some of the modifying methods of the type. After these have been called, the type will become effectively level 1 immutable.
      Default:
      ""
